    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Bloodlines is a Creature breeder and Auto battler with a lot of depth where you get to build and refine your battle teams to fight against other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275890/extras/8747f810076c7752005db51ac3945f27.webp?t=1734015878\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275890/extras/8747f810076c7752005db51ac3945f27.poster.avif?t=1734015878\" class=\"bb_img\" width=200 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breed Creatures with unique stats, skills or forms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Selectively breed the offspring to strengthen them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the Ultimate team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight other players teams in asynchronous multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win items to influence the offspring. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine your Bloodlines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 24 different creature breeds with their own unique unlockable skill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 80 unique Items to help you breed </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rank up to find better Items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >breed rare colour variants</p></li></ul>",
